          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "\"This thing is amazing.\"",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_pM69x7": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>\"I have been a dance teacher for many years and<strong> my knees are definitely not what they used to be</strong>. This Knee massager is <strong>fantastic and not only provides relief during the process but also increases mobility after the fact. 10 mins on each knee once a day and I already notice a difference. Well worth it\"</strong></p>"
