    "rich_text_aHrm9n": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_iF9cgM": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do You Relate?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_GJETWy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Imagine being able to<strong> relieve your chronic pains, stiffness, swelling</strong> <strong>from </strong>the comfort of <strong>your home – in just a few minutes</strong> – <strong>without </strong>taking <strong>painkillers</strong> or <strong>expensive  lengthy therapy</strong>…<br/><br/><strong>There is so much more out there in life</strong>, however it requires mobility, no one wants to carry one another. Everyone wants to enjoy the beauty of life and its special moments. It requires moving, <strong>having somthing in which prevents the moving is a big problem.</strong><br/><br/>Premium Heals isn't just a store for your health, its a team that solved the problem, from what started as issues in all our families to trying everything from A-Z, surgeries, therapy, medication, and so much more. <strong>We lost some important people in our lives. We don't want that for you and your loved ones.</strong></p><p><strong>It took a while until we found the solutions, trial after trial. Product researches, doctors and so much time. We finally found somthing...</strong></p><p><strong>For the first time in moderation, your able to heal your problems from the good of your home without the need of</strong> taking drugs, spending time for therapy that would throw you if you didn't pay and surgeries that simply put you out for as long as its needed. <br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_iF9cgM",
        "text_GJETWy"
      ],
      "disabled": true,
      "name": "t:sections.rich-text.presets.name",
      "settings": {
