          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>\"This is one of the best things I’ve bought in a long time.\"</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_MFJ6EF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>I'm a sixty one year old carpenter/building contractor , <strong>knees are bone on bone, left one became so stiff couldn't bend it , have been waiting for knee replacement for two years</strong>, I received the Ultra Knee Massager and used on each knee for the auto timed <strong>10 minutes, saw results immediately</strong>, been using for a week now and have <strong>had three friends with knee problems try mine and all three have noticed some relief after only 1 minutes and have all ordered one. relief is absolutely amazing.</strong></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
